		<h3>echo::system</h3>
		<p> 
echo::system is a performance of 'constructed' environments with live music, dance, live video and electro-acoustic design. Performers and viewers co-exist within a sensory rich, immersive environment, witnessing stories that unfold as a way to re-examine contemporary urban life. Led by Grisha Coleman and Todd Ingalls.<br/>
<br/>
