		<h3>DC Game Club</h3>
		<p> 
DC Game Club is a community for game designers of any skill level from total newbies to seasoned experts.  Interested in skills like 3D modeling in Blender, game design in Unity, or sound design with Audacity? Interested in connecting with collaborators to work on a new project?  Tired of toiling in isolation?!  Join us!  The gathering is informal. No lectures or presentations, just an ad hoc group of people sharing their knowledge and looking over each other's shoulders. Bring your laptop and grab a chair.  If you don't have a laptop, come anyways, we'll hook you up. Led by David Birchfield.<br/>
<br/>
		</p>
	
