		<p>
Learning Installation is a platform for creating media rich, augmented displays for printed display installations. The project combines high quality physical prints, rich interactive media, realtime video object tracking and new mobile computing devices to create an engaging collaborative media experience. Led by David Tinapple and Loren Olson.<br/>
<br/>
